        </item>
        <item>
            <title>中国法院判 Apple 未有滥用市场支配地位，正式驳回诉讼</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/chinaapple-monopoly/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chinaapple-monopoly</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/chinaapple-monopoly/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 07:35:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[App Store]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[垄断]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239273</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 于 2021 年被一名中国大陆 Apple 用户以「滥用市场支配地位」为由，将 Apple （中国大陆）起诉至法院。Apple 用户金鑫指控 Apple 在 App Store 收取 30% 的佣金，且只接受 Apple Pay 的支付方式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1239282 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1x1-1-694x463.jpg" alt="China iPhone users" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1x1-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1x1-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-22/apple-aapl-fans-in-china-rush-to-buy-iphone-15-despite-government-ban-huawei">彭博社</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 用户金鑫表示在购买爱奇艺、喜马拉雅、网易云音乐和懂球帝的会员服务时发现，Apple 平台上的定价均比 Android 平台高，且只能选择 Apple Pay 的支付方式。他指因为 Apple 的垄断，他丧失了支付方式的选择权。Apple 公司规定开发人员须向 Apple 支付交易额 30% 俗称「苹果税」的佣金，所以 Apple 平台的定价往往比 Android 高，他必须被逼接受不公平的高定价。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">中国法院指 Apple 在中国软件市场的确具有支配地位，但认为并未有滥用其地位，近日正式驳回诉讼。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantf/20240530/1717041124904/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E9%A7%81%E5%9B%9E%E5%B0%8D%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Capp-store%E6%94%B6%E4%BD%A3%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2iDek1zWYyGt4jcoD9FJlWW458Qh8sHQ5wkAYHjMGhomsH_BfRlLDukzg_aem_AYh_ajadY2ZyhCyo2vC9x_2JjIcSyXXDNOVhcGx_kHkMAHmJF8o3Yddsz3-GASkqiGZd6M8MKtIGCc-_oIhQAQQG">明报</a>、<a href="https://tw.stock.yahoo.com/news/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91%E5%AE%98%E5%8F%B8%E5%8B%9D%E8%A8%B4-234013553.html">Yahoo 奇摩股市</a>、<a href="https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11496661">澎湃新闻</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2022/11/18/business/apple-foxconn-china.html">The New York Times</a><br /><b>相关文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/14/ipad-pro-m4-reivew/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】iPad Pro M4 版本，实测效能、剪片速度、Apple Pencil Pro 新功能</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/lego-ideas-apple-store/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LEGO 粉丝特别设计，神还原 Apple Store 积木套装</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/samsung-galaxy-watch-x/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Samsung Galaxy Watch X   传 6 月底发表以 Apple Watch Ultra 作假想敌</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/chinaapple-monopoly/fun-tech/">中国法院判 Apple 未有滥用市场支配地位，正式驳回诉讼</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/chinaapple-monopoly/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
